\begin{center}\large Executive Summary\end{center}
\vspace{0.5em}
RGS Construction Lesotho (Pty) Ltd invites Halso to participate in an equity partnership (R5,000,000 for 20% equity) to supply gas exclusively for our ECO Homes programmes in Lesotho and the Limpopo pilot. This document combines the acceptance letter, investment deck content, project timeline, and the authoritative financial CSVs located under the Financials folder.

