\input{Merged_Partnership_Proposal.md}

\clearpage
\section{Investment Deck (slide text)}
\begin{itemize}
  \item Title slide: RGS Construction Lesotho — Eco-Friendly Housing Project
  \item The Problem: Housing shortage, Limpopo context
  \item Our Solution: Modular eco-homes, integrated gas
  \item Market Opportunity and Business Model
  \item Traction, Impact and Team
  \item The Ask: R5,000,000 for 20% equity; 20-year exclusivity agreement for Halso
\end{itemize}

\clearpage
\section{Project Plan and Timeline}
Assumptions: Receipt of R5,000,000 by end-February 2026; 3 months for legal and BCG site visits and initial allocation. Phased rollout commencing June 2026.
\begin{itemize}
  \item Feb 2026: Investment receipt and BCG fee settlement
  \item Mar--May 2026: MoU, governance, due diligence
  \item Jun--Dec 2026: Phase 1, 1,000 units
  \item 2027--2030: Ramp to 9,000 units (Limpopo pilot)
  \item 2026--2035: Lesotho scale to 90,000 homes (10-year phased rollout)
\end{itemize}

\clearpage
