\section{Risks, Mitigations and Next Steps}
\begin{itemize}
  \item Key risks: interest/loan terms, construction timeline, regulatory and permitting delays, currency and inflation risk.
  \item Mitigations: phased drawdown, strong governance, early community engagement, conservative financial buffers.
  \item Next steps: finalise MoU, complete due diligence, appoint solicitors, BCG tranche schedule, sign equity agreement, and begin phased rollout.
\end{itemize}

